	<h1>.eco Sustainability Policy</h1>

	<div class="content-section">
		<em>Updated: November 13, 2024</em>
	</div>

 	<div class="content-section">
		<p><a href="https://bigroom.eco">Big Room Inc.</a> is the registry for the .eco domain, the online home for the global environmental community. As an active member of the community, we are working to build an eco-friendly internet and a better world.</p>

		<p>We having formalized our commitment to environmental and social action by becoming a <a href="/news/eco-is-certified-b-corp/">Certified B Corporation</a>.</p>

		<p>We are the world's first <a href="/news/eco-is-carbon-neutral/">carbon neutral domain registry</a> certified under PAS 2060. This means that this means that any emissions associated with managing .eco domain names is accounted for and offset. We are committed to reporting regularly on our environmental impacts.</p>

		<p>We believe that by working with like-minded people and organizations throughout the .eco community, we can collectively act to reduce waste, water, energy use, and greenhouse gas emissions.</p>

	</div>

